PLAYER HELP
UNFOLLOW
In order to stop following somebody, the command is ~CCOMunfollow~CDEF. You
can either unfollow a single person from the list of people you are
following, or you can simply ~CCOMunfollow all~CDEF to clear the entire
list.

You can see who you are following by typing ~CCOMleaders~CHLP.

See also: ~CREFfollow~CHLP, ~CREFlose~CHLP
